<i>noun</i>: 해설 [해ː설], 심사평 [심사평] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>해설 [해ː설]</dt><br>
<dd>explanation; interpretation; commentary</dd><br>
<dd>어려운 문제나 사건의 내용 등을 알기 쉽게 풀어 설명함. 또는 그런 글이나 책.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of explaining a tricky or complex problem or case to another person in terms easily understandable, or such a text or book.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>심사평 [심사평]</dt><br>
<dd>commentary; evaluation result</dd><br>
<dd>잘하고 못한 것을 가리기 위해 자세히 살펴 내린 평가. 또는 그 평가를 쓴 글.</dd><br>
<dd>The evaluation made after a close look at someone or something to decide whether it or he/she is good or bad, or the piece of writing which contains the evaluation.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>